<h1>13. The Collective Architecture</h1>
<p>A single hemisphere has fixed computational dimensionality. The collective — cascaded hemispheres each specializing through ferroelectric learning — is the scaling answer. Inter-hemisphere coupling remains an open design gap with no proposed solution. The collective architecture is downstream of demonstrating a single hemisphere works.</p>

