<h2>24.8  Sequencing</h2>
<p>Decoherence simulation is downstream of P3, not parallel to it. The finite-size recurrence problem may render Betsy unsuitable for decoherence simulation regardless of reservoir computing performance — the two applications may fail for independent reasons. This is a weaker sequencing argument than stated in earlier drafts, and is stated here as corrected.</p>

